name: C series 004: The Nest
description:
‘Jj’ THE WINDOW CLEANER came across this nest when he was up in the east district working his magic on some glass day dreaming of a world where he could make a good living through his art instead of this daily grind...
He heard a chirping sound and there they were.  He got down pretty sharpish and called for the exterminators.  Nothing quite as terrifying as an angry mother viper owl…
